Class LoggingWebDriverEventListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openqa.selenium.support.events.AbstractWebDriverEventListener
      • ch.vorburger.webdriver.reporting.LoggingWebDriverEventListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.openqa.selenium.support.events.WebDriverEventListener

    public class LoggingWebDriverEventListener
extends org.openqa.selenium.support.events.AbstractWebDriverEventListener
    A WebDriverEventListener which logs method calls. This class should not have any JUnit or I/O dependencies/imports, only WebDriver.
    Author:
    Michael Vorburger
